name: Rickety Rocket!
description:
Play as a skilled pilot. 

 

Avoid many obstacles as you navigate the level and make from launch pad to the next landing pad. 

Total of 5 levels; try to beat them all!



Controls:

  • Spacebar to thrust
  • a/d or left/right arrows to steer the rocket

This is my rendition of the Project Boost project as part of the "Complete C# Unity Developer 3D: Learn to Code Making Games" course.
